title: ‘We May Have Overestimated His Anger Management Skills’
text: Megyn Kelly has said that she and her network may have overestimated the anger management skills of Donald Trump ahead of the infamous debate that kicked off a feud between the Fox News host and the popular Republican presidential candidate.
